ZH: 我们家的核桃树结了很多核桃。
EN: The walnut tree in our backyard has produced a lot of walnuts.

ZH: 核桃是一种营养丰富的坚果。
EN: Walnuts are a nutritious type of nut.

ZH: 春天是核桃树的开花季节。
EN: Spring is the season when walnut trees bloom.

ZH: 奶奶喜欢用核桃做菜。
EN: Grandma likes to cook with walnuts.

ZH: 酱料中加入一些核桃会让菜肴更加美味。
EN: Adding some walnuts to the sauce will make the dish even more delicious.

ZH: 听说核桃对大脑发育有益。
EN: I've heard that walnuts are beneficial for brain development.

ZH: 核桃还可以用来炸鸡肉。
EN: Walnuts can also be used to fry chicken.

ZH: 学校附近有一家核桃专卖店。
EN: There is a walnut specialty store near the school.

ZH: 这个核桃很新鲜，可以直接吃。
EN: This walnut is very fresh and can be eaten directly.

ZH: 周末去果园摘些核桃吃吧。
EN: Let's go to the orchard to pick some walnuts to eat on the weekend.

