EN: Walnut shells can be made into a type of pigment.

ZH: 爸爸喜欢在晚饭后吃几颗核桃。
EN: Dad likes to eat a few walnuts after dinner.

ZH: 姐姐用核桃壳制作了一幅画。
EN: My older sister made a painting using walnut shells.

ZH: 核桃里有很多的营养因子。
EN: Walnuts contain many nutrients.

ZH: 孩子们在果树下玩捡核桃。
EN: The children play under the fruit tree, picking up walnuts.

ZH: 昨天吃了一块核桃巧克力。
EN: I had a piece of walnut chocolate yesterday.

ZH: 核桃酱可以搭配水果一起吃。
EN: Walnut butter can be eaten with fruit.

ZH: 这个饼干里的核桃味道很浓。
EN: The walnut flavor in this cookie is very strong.

ZH: 核桃是一种高脂食品。
EN: Walnuts are a high-fat food.

ZH: 我不喜欢核桃的味道。
EN: I don't like the taste of walnuts.
